<br>
Through a lot of shuffling and looking for regular drops (like Spind drops), I was able to get (at level 50 with some epiuc gear swapped out):<br>
<br>
Thrust 18<br>
Heat 20<br>
Cold 26<br>
Spirit 24<br>
Body 24<br>
Matter 23<br>
Energy 26<br>
HP 170<br>
<br>
I can max HP and Heat by letting Body/Matter suffer at 14/13.<br>
At L50, resists are capped at 26% and hp at +200.<br>
This config maxes str/con, but dex/quick suffer a lot.<br>
<br>
